Class DefaultAbstractUseCase

java.lang.Object
  com.jdroid.android.usecase.AbstractUseCase<DefaultUseCaseListener>
      com.jdroid.android.usecase.DefaultAbstractUseCase
All Implemented Interfaces:
UseCase<DefaultUseCaseListener>, Serializable, Runnable
Direct Known Subclasses:
FacebookAuthenticationUseCase, GooglePlusAuthenticationUseCase, PaginatedUseCase
public abstract class DefaultAbstractUseCase
extends AbstractUseCase<DefaultUseCaseListener>

Abstract use case that handles the calls to DefaultUseCaseListener.onStartUseCase(), DefaultUseCaseListener.onFinishUseCase(), DefaultUseCaseListener.onFinishCanceledUseCase() and DefaultUseCaseListener.onFinishFailedUseCase(RuntimeException) when executing.

Author:
Maxi Rosson
